ActCanada-Newfoundland Atlantic Accord Implementation Act
PrecisAppointment of W. WAYNE THISTLE of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, as a panel member for the selection of a Chairman of the Canada-Newfoundland Offshore Petroleum Board, for a term beginning September 1, 2005 and ending on the earlier of the day the panel selects a Chairman of the Board in accordance with subsection 12(2) of the Act, and the day that the federal and provincial governments agree on the appointment of the Chairman of the Board.
